Titolo: Beyond Oasis

Anno: 1994

Descrizione: Beyond Oasis, known in Europe as The Story of Thor, is an action-adventure game developed by Ancient and published by Sega for the Sega Genesis. The game has also been re-released in various emulated collections, such as the Virtual Console, Sonic's Ultimate Genesis Collection, and Sega Forever. A prequel to the game, The Legend of Oasis, was released for the Sega Saturn in 1996.